Title: Let Them Eat Cake
Plot: The team takes on the case of a fitness guru on an all-natural diet who collapsed while filming a video. Meanwhile, Foreman conducts Huntington's Disease drug trials and Thirteen signs on as a subject, Cuddy is forced to move into House's office, and Kutner uses House's name to run an online medical-advice website.
GuestStars: Becky Baeling, Brad Grunberg, David Lengel, Christopher Stapleton, Nicole Cannon, Lori Petty, Julia Putnam, Danielle Petty
